#ROOMS
#9400
The Shattered Gate~
The towering iron gates of Kel'Shadra lie shattered and bent, torn from their
hinges by some ancient and terrible force. Beyond them yawns the darkness of
a crypt that has not seen living feet in centuries. The stonework is cracked
and weeping with black moisture, and runes of binding have been forcibly
broken from the archway overhead. A faint, sickly phosphorescence clings to
the walls, just enough to reveal the horror of what lies ahead. The path
south leads deeper into the crypts.~
