E
gate runes archway~
The binding runes were carved by the ancient order of Kel'Shadra to seal
whatever nightmares lurk within. They have been shattered from the inside.
~
S
#9401
The Entry Hall of Lamentations~
The entry hall stretches before you in grim grandeur, its vaulted ceiling
lost in shadow above. Along the walls are carved bas-reliefs depicting the
final moments of those who were sealed within -- faces frozen in expressions
of absolute terror. The floor is cracked obsidian, polished by centuries of
dark rituals. Iron sconces still hold black candles that burn with cold blue
flame, though no mortal lit them. Exits lead north back to the gate, east
into a nave, west toward a vestibule, and south deeper into the complex.~
