The altar of black glass reflects not what is in the room, but something
else -- a dark, inverted reflection of a place you do not recognize.
~
E
seal ritual diagram~
The ritual seal appears to be a binding circle. At its center, a single
word is inscribed that you cannot quite read -- your eyes slide away from
it whenever you try to focus.
~
S
#9404
The Dark Chancel~
Beyond the nave, the chancel is a place of concentrated malevolence. The
ceiling here is painted with a mural of the night sky, but the stars are
wrong -- arranged in patterns that suggest terrible geometries. A massive
obsidian sarcophagus dominates the center of the room, its lid shifted
slightly to one side, suggesting something crawled out long ago. Heavy chains
are secured to the sarcophagus but they too have been broken. The path south
leads back to the nave, and a passage descends down.~
