sarcophagus obsidian~
The sarcophagus bears no name. Instead, a long epitaph in the shadow-tongue
reads: 'Laid here not in rest but in restraint. That which was bound here
endures beyond death, beyond ending. If you have found this place, it is
already too late.'
~
