#9407
The Hall of Mirrors~
The corridor opens into a wide hall lined with tall mirrors set in tarnished
silver frames. The mirrors do not show accurate reflections -- instead, each
one shows a different version of you: one covered in wounds, one standing
victorious over a heap of bones, one consumed by shadow, one simply absent,
the mirror showing only an empty room. The floor is marked with four symbols.
You may exit north back to the corridor or south.~
