#9408
The Chamber of Whispers~
A perfectly circular chamber where the acoustics are supernatural. Any sound
made here is amplified and distorted, transformed into voices speaking in
languages you do not know. The walls are covered in writing -- not carved but
burned, as if by dark energy from within. At the center of the chamber is a
stone pedestal with an indentation shaped like a hand. The exits are north
and south, and a sealed door to the east.~
