#9410
The Gallery of the Fallen~
A long gallery displaying portraits of those who founded the order of
Kel'Shadra, each framed in bone. As you walk past, their painted eyes
seem to follow you with expressions of sorrow and warning. The floor here
has partially given way, and crossing it requires care -- some boards are
missing, revealing a darkness below that produces sounds of breathing. A
door stands at the far south end, and the exit north returns to the antechamber.~
