#9412
The Antechamber of Darkness~
The bottom of the great stair opens into an antechamber bathed in total
darkness, save for a ring of green-flamed torches that burn waist high.
The air here is thick and tastes of iron and old death. The walls press
close and the ceiling is very high, lost in shadow. You can feel things
watching you from beyond the torch-light. Exits lead up to the threshold,
north into the labyrinth, east and west.~
