#9413
The Labyrinth Entrance~
You stand at the entrance to the great labyrinth of Kel'Shadra. The walls
of the maze rise twenty feet high, carved from volcanic stone worn smooth
by ages of dark energy. The passages twist immediately in multiple directions,
designed to confuse. Above the entrance arch, a warning is carved: 'The
labyrinth remembers all who enter. Not all of what it remembers is friendly.'
