#9423
The Labyrinth - The Echo Chamber~
A roughly spherical chamber where sounds echo with impossible complexity,
creating layered harmonics. Speaking aloud here causes your own voice to
be returned in fragments over the course of several minutes, mixed with
other voices that were here long before you. The chamber has no purpose
that is immediately apparent, but the echoes themselves seem to contain
information. The exit east returns to the junction.~
