#9424
The Ritual Chamber of Binding~
The end goal of those who built the labyrinth: a vast circular chamber with
a ritual circle of power that fills the entire floor, inscribed with thousands
of runes. At the center stands an altar of pure black stone atop which rests
an ancient tome sealed with seven locks. The power in this room is palpable
and crushing. The air shimmers slightly, as though reality itself is under
strain here. The exit north returns to the antechamber below.~
