#9429
The Final Sanctum~
The deepest room of the Crypts of Kel'Shadra. A vast chamber, cathedral-like,
where the architecture reaches its apex of dark grandeur. The floor here is
living shadow, shifting and writhing underfoot. The ceiling is so high it
cannot be seen. At the chamber's center, suspended in a cage of black iron,
is the entity that the entire crypt was built to contain: an ancient darkness
that has waited here for centuries, patient beyond mortal understanding.
It is aware of you. It has always been aware of you. The exit north returns.~
