The Deep Ossuary~
Far below the main crypt level, this chamber is the repository of those
who were sacrificed during the construction and consecration of the crypt.
Thousands of bones are stacked in precise geometric arrangements that form
patterns only visible from the ceiling. A raised dais at the center holds
nothing -- but the outline of something large was placed there for a long
time, the stone worn smooth around it. Passages lead up through the labyrinth
above and east.~
